casebody.data:
No. 58,

Misc.

Lyons v. Klatte, State Hospital Superintendent. Petitioner pro se. Thomas C. Lynch, Attorney General of California, and Robert R. Granucci and Jay S. Linderman, Deputy Attorneys General, for respondent.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari is denied.
